Sentencas: The perovskite (La0.75Sr0.25) Cr0.5Mn0.5O3 (LSCM) is shown to be an effective, redox-stable electrode that can be used for both cathode and anode SOFC operation, to provide a symmetrical fuel cell system with good performance characteristics.
Titulo: A symmetrical solid oxide fuel cell demonstrating redox stable perovskite electrodes
